<div class="how-to-use page-width section-padding">
  <div class="header">
    <h1>{{ section.settings.title }}</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      Our premium freeze-dried fruits are incredibly versatile and can enhance many of your favorite foods and drinks.
      Here are some delicious ways to incorporate them into your daily routine!
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="illustration-container">
    <img src="{{ 'how-to-use-illustration.png' | asset_url }}" alt="How to use illustration" class="illustration-image">
  </div>

  <div class="usage-section">
    <div class="usage-card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="icon smoothie-icon"></div>
        <h3>Smoothies & Shakes</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="description">Add our freeze-dried fruits to your smoothies and shakes for an intense burst of flavor and a nutritional boost. They blend perfectly and dissolve to create a smooth texture with vibrant taste.</p>
      <ul class="instructions">
        <li>Add 1-2 tablespoons to your blender</li>
        <li>Great with yogurt, milk, or plant-based alternatives</li>
        <li>Blends instantly - no need to rehydrate first</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="usage-card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="icon dessert-icon"></div>
        <h3>Dessert Toppings</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="description">Sprinkle over ice cream, yogurt, oatmeal, or cereal for a delightful crunch and natural sweetness. The vivid colors make any dessert look spectacular!</p>
      <ul class="instructions">
        <li>Crush slightly for a more even distribution</li>
        <li>Try mixing with nuts for contrasting textures</li>
        <li>Perfect for decorating cakes and cupcakes</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="usage-card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="icon baking-icon"></div>
        <h3>Baking & Cooking</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="description">Incorporate into your baking for colorful, flavorful additions to muffins, pancakes, cookies, and more. The freeze-dried texture means they won't add excess moisture to your recipes.</p>
      <ul class="instructions">
        <li>Fold gently into batters and doughs</li>
        <li>Can be powdered for natural food coloring</li>
        <li>Use as-is or rehydrate depending on your recipe</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="usage-card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="icon trail-icon"></div>
        <h3>Trail Mix & Snacks</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="description">Create your own custom trail mix with nuts, seeds, and our freeze-dried fruits. The light weight makes them perfect for hiking, traveling, or just enjoying as a healthy snack any time.</p>
      <ul class="instructions">
        <li>Mix with nuts and dark chocolate for a balanced energy boost</li>
        <li>Store in small containers for portion control</li>
        <li>Perfect on-the-go snack for kids and adults</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="tips-section">
    <h2>Pro Tips for Best Results</h2>
    <ul class="tips-list">
      <li>
        <strong>Storage:</strong> Always reseal the package properly and store in a cool, dry place to maintain the crisp texture.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Rehydration:</strong> For some recipes, you may want to rehydrate the fruits. Simply soak in warm water for 5-10 minutes until they reach your desired texture.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Powdering:</strong> Use a food processor or spice grinder to create fruit powders that can be used as natural food coloring or flavor enhancers.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Pairing:</strong> Our freeze-dried fruits pair exceptionally well with dairy, chocolate, and nuts, creating a perfect balance of flavors and textures.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  {% if section.settings.show_recipe %}
    <div class="recipe-idea">
      <h2>Featured Recipe: Tropical Breakfast Parfait</h2>
      <div class="recipe-content">
        <div class="ingredients">
          <h4>Ingredients:</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>½ cup Greek yogurt</li>
            <li>¼ cup granola</li>
            <li>1 tbsp honey</li>
            <li>2 tbsp Freeze-Dried Jackfruit</li>
            <li>1 tbsp Freeze-Dried Custard Apple</li>
            <li>Optional: fresh mint for garnish</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="instructions">
          <h4>Instructions:</h4>
          <ol>
            <li>Layer Greek yogurt in the bottom of a glass or bowl</li>
            <li>Add a layer of granola</li>
            <li>Sprinkle freeze-dried fruits on top</li>
            <li>Drizzle with honey</li>
            <li>Repeat layers as desired</li>
            <li>Enjoy immediately for maximum crunch!</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  {% endif %}
</div>

<style>
  .how-to-use {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .header h1 {
    color: var(--color-primary-3);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 2rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--color-grey-5);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .illustration-container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .illustration-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .usage-section {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .usage-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .usage-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .icon {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-right: 1rem;
    background-position: center;
    background-size: 30px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .smoothie-icon, .dessert-icon, .baking-icon, .trail-icon {
    background-color: rgba(64, 206, 181, 0.15);
  }

  /* Add background images for icons */

  .description {
    color: var(--color-grey-5);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .instructions {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-grey-3);
  }

  .instructions li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .tips-section {
    background: var(--color-primary-10);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-primary-5);
  }

  .tips-section h2 {
    color: var(--color-primary-1);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .tips-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .tips-list li {
    color: var(--color-grey-3);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .tips-list strong {
    color: var(--color-primary-5);
  }

  .recipe-idea {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border-left: 5px solid var(--color-primary-5);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .recipe-idea h2 {
    color: var(--color-primary-3);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .recipe-content {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .recipe-content h4 {
    color: var(--color-primary-5);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .usage-section {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .recipe-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 992px) {
    .usage-section {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "How To Use Page",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "title",
      "label": "Page Title",
      "default": "Creative Ways to Enjoy Freeze-Dried Fruits"
    },
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_recipe",
      "label": "Show Recipe Section",
      "default": true
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "How To Use Page",
      "category": "Custom"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}